lead_paragraph: Arsenal's problems mounted as their latest stumble in the Premier League title race on Wednesday was compounded by news goalkeeper Petr Cech will miss Saturday's match against arch-rivals Tottenham Hotspur.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Problems Mount as Cech Ruled Out of Spurs Game
